    <Step id="e71bbd8c-34d3-4216-a5af-2d5a9a5d9139" name="There are certain situations and factors that put people at risk of abuse..... " title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;If one or more factors are present, it may increase the possibility of abuse occurring:-&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Adult at risk living in an isolated situation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Where an adult is dependant on others for their personal and practical care.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;The carer has a lack of support network.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Where a carer does not have the necessary understanding of the condition of the vulnerable adult that would enable them to offer appropriate and effective care.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;A previous history of abuse.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Where the vulnerable person exhibits demanding or challenging behaviour.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Inappropriate physical or emotional environment e.g. lack of privacy and personal space.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;The carer has difficulties such as debt, alcohol or mental health problems.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" intro="true">
